summary:
It's Taylor Tuesday again and I thought I'd share with you some of my thoughts from over the weekend. 
I was driving to the...
body:
It’s Taylor Tuesday again and I thought I’d share with you some of my thoughts from over the weekend.

I was driving to the library Saturday afternoon and had the radio on. Delicate came on and I was all like OMGasdfghjkl!!!!! All the memories of experiencing this song live came over me. Then I started thinking about all of the people that are listening to the radio and hearing this song as a local and have so manyyyyyy questions! Like…

Are the other listeners aware who is singing this song?

Are they feeling it?

Are they turning up the volume?

Is this the first time they are hearing it?

I wonder what it’s like for them?

tags: how to get away with murder
summary: So i am kind of known for having wild dreams and last night i dreamt that i was one of annalise keating's students and we all...
body:
So i am kind of known for having wild dreams and last night i dreamt that i was one of annalise keating’s students and we all broke into her house because we were trying to find evidence of her doing something- who knows what!- but she ended up coming home and yelling at us all. AND THEN. SOMEHOW. NEXT THING I KNOW. My dream switched somehow?? And i was at a taylor swift secret session????????

Taylor said she saw me on tumblr and i was like ?????? How!! And we made her famous chai sugar cookies and she wanted one-on-one time with all of us so when it was my turn we sat in the kitchen and she was making a pasta and veggie dish for us and i was telling her all about myself. I was like “so i’m in college and i also work full time…. ugh wait no i’m not in college anymore i am just working… but i actually am taking some classes….. i’m 18…. no wait i’m like 20 something but i cant remember how old i am oh my god!” And taylor was like “it’s okay i know all about you” and i was like HOWwWwWwwwW and i never even got to tell her thank you for being amazing or how long i have loved her or how important she is to my life. I just babbled like an idiot and i realize that probably my only chance to meet taylor was last night in my ~wildest dream~ (lol) and i even fucked that up! But i just had to share hahaha. Even in my sleep she is perfect 😍
